            },
            "description": "Creates the ANF target volume in migration mode. The request body must include `\"migrationVolume\": true` in the `dataProtection` properties to indicate this volume will receive data from an external ONTAP source via the Migration as a Service feature.\n\nThe operation is asynchronous. A `201 Created` or `202 Accepted` response will include an `Azure-AsyncOperation` header URL — save this value to the `ma.Azure-AsyncOperationID` environment variable before running the next step.\n\n**Required variables:** `apicloudurl`, `subscriptionId`, `resourceGroupName`, `accountName`, `poolName`, `ma.volumeName`, `vol.subnetId`, `vol.usageThreshold`, `vol.protocolTypes`, `serviceLevel`, `api-version`"
          },
